    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1919-09-10T17:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1919-09-10T17:00:00-05:00" n="744"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d744">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.00/5155: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in Great Britain</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_DJW1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Davis</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-09-10T18:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 10, 1919, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>5946. Repeat your 2972, September 5, 6 p.m.<note n="64" xml:id="d744fn64">Not
                        printed.</note> and 2903, August 27, 3 p.m. containing reports from
                    Archangel, to American Mission with following message for <persName
                        corresp="#p_PFL">Polk</persName>: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“In spite of our own withdrawal and definite evacuation of British, is
                            Council of Four contemplating any measures to steady or support what
                            appears to be genuine popular movement in Archangel district?”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_PW1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
